Hierophant of Phalanx<br>
<a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=67039>See my 
stuff!</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utetriancorbec.showPublicProfile?language=EN>tetrian corbec</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Finally Housebroken!</span><br>  Posts: 396<br> <font color=#333399>(7/10/02 10:20:54 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26421.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Equipment advice please</span><hr size=1> Get your dragon faction up and make the talisman of benevolence(takes 1 high level group 30 mins to do)<br>
<br>
if you do faction in the arena area with some other people you might even get a few leather quest pieces for thurgadin :)<br>
<br>
Once you get the talisman, change your two rings to 6ac 65hp ones(eventually get a shadel bandit ring, depending on funds)<br>
<br>
New shield of sorts - not quite sure whats the best here, but the crystal chiting shield, or the orc oracle shield thingy from orcs in EW would be nice, sarnak battle shield also, but you would loose some wisdom on that.<br>
<br>
Maybe replace bracers with some blue diamond stuff for ressists(depending on funds also) <p><p><B>Tetrian Corbec</B><br>60 Druid 
<A HREF=http://www.Mortalis.com/forum>Mortalis</A><br>

<A HREF=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=3403>Profile</A></p><font size="2" face="Times New Roman"></font><br>

</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utetriancorbec.showPublicProfile?language=EN>tetrian corbec</A> at: 7/10/02 10:27:47 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uelethiomeltimberfall.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ElethiomelTimberfall</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Puppy</span><br>  Posts: 88<br> <font color=#333399>(7/10/02 2:06:20 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26421.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Equipment advice please</span><hr size=1> replace the BIC with a prayer shawl and get a Crystalline Torque.  Get Elysian BP, hat, legs, arms (or just do full suit like me :-)  Consider doing thurg bracer quest.  Get either coldain skin or grey flesh gloves.  Do the Shield of Bane Warding quest (my next step).  Get serious about your Epic, it's a great item, and you can solo a lot of the camps. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uelethiomeltimberfall.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ElethiomelTimberfall</A> at: 7/10/02 2:11:35 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/unatalisrainswift.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Natalis Rainswift</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Puppy</span><br>  Posts: 5<br> <font color=#333399>(7/10/02 3:30:12 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26421.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Equipment advice please</span><hr size=1> Wow! Good advice :) I've been trying to do the Talisman of Benevolence, but I can never catch the Scout while she's up. What is this Elysian stuff you speak of? I've never heard of it. Is it the new tailored armor? <br>
<br>
I've camped Kael on and off for a long time, but I still haven't got any leather drops :( I will try to get a bracer though. Coldain gloves sould like a good start too. I have a full set of resist gear I share with my cleric, so I have the BD stuff covered. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uelethiomeltimberfall.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ElethiomelTimberfall</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Puppy</span><br>  Posts: 93<br> <font color=#333399>(7/10/02 4:12:42 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26421.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Equipment advice please</span><hr size=1> Elysian armor drops from Disturbed Elysian Remains in Umbral Plains.  Some pieces are much better stat-wise than our Velious armor.  No clickies though.<br>
 <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uelethiomeltimberfall.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ElethiomelTimberfall</A> at: 7/10/02 4:13:07 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ualuaeia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aluaeia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Just got my shots!</span><br>  Posts: 104<br> <font color=#333399>(7/10/02 5:20:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26421.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Equipment advice please</span><hr size=1> Elysian is the druid only chain look armor that drops in Umbral Plains.  Easily soloable at 53 with Warden symbol and thurg bracer (or ES arms) without epic (but need KEI).<br>
<br>
Anyways, IMHO Warden Symbol of Tunare would be an upgrade for you. (clickable root is especially useful when you're oom and get agro'd).<br>
<br>
Supple Scale Armband (bracer), has Extended Range III focus now, so even better.  (no drop from Drolvarg Warlord in KC, get a group there or ask group there to tell if one is going to rot)<br>
<br>
Brown Chitin Legs, Shadel Bandit Ring and Tattered Hide Cloak from Fungus Grove. (buy or get a group, shiknar, bandits and dregs drop respectively)<br>
<br>
The aforementioned Coldain Skin Gloves, or Grey Flesh Gloves.<br>
<br>
Enshrouded Veil from HS unless you find the mithril mask's focus to be useful.  (you'd gain 2 ac 30 hp 10 sv fire and summoning efficiency III focus, and when you factor in the 5 post-200 wis loss vs the 30 mana increase, you gain 1 point of mana, lol)<br>
<br>
Shroud of Nature from Droga (or the currently bugged Nurga), soloable, I let 3 rot while doing some Chardok faction back in 52. =/<br>
<br>
Othmir Fur Cap (player-tailored), should be cheap since they're one of the easier tailoring skill routes post-200.<br>
<br>
Obulus Death Shroud from Sebilis. (expensive nowadays, but the focus effect is worth it)  or Elder Wolf Hide from Ghowlik in Hollowshade Moor (unknown drop rate, I got 2 out of 2 kills, but this was like a week after Luclin opened)<br>
<br>
Ceremonial Smudging Stick from Hollowshade Moor when the Grimlings have control of their village, drops off Chieftain (permarooted, with 2 healers in the tent behind him that are pullable and 2 guards next to him that are pullable and add when you go to loot chieftain)<br>
<br>
Diamond Wedding Band from Tower of Frozen Shadow 5th floor (wedding).  Easily soloable *if* you have keys, otherwise it's a PITA to get the keys solo, especially the one to the third floor.<br>
<br>
Dark Ember from Firbrand the Black in EW (rare drop), soloable<br>
<br>
Bone Bladed Scimitar from Hierophant Grazan in The Grey, soloable, uncommon drop. <p>Aluaeia Evangelion
<br>Level 55 Fier`dal Preserver of Tunare
<br>Tarew Marr
<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=39316">My Magelo Profile</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/unatalisrainswift.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Natalis Rainswift</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Puppy</span><br>  Posts: 7<br> <font color=#333399>(7/11/02 2:38:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26421.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Equipment advice please</span><hr size=1> I will soon be heading to UP to try for Elysian armor :) I have a perma-group, with a 60 chanter, and a 58 monk, 54 cleric so that should go well.<br>
<br>
I tried long ago when the Tunare symbol quest came out to get the symbol, but back then LFay was crawling with HT mobs. Oww.<br>
<br>
I've been camping KC (I so hate that place) for the supple scale armband a lot for my cleric, and still haven't seen one drop. <br>
<br>
I'll look into camping FG again, for that stuff. I should be able to get a ring quickly. I don't know about the other stuff.<br>
<br>
Instead of the Enshrouded Veil, maybe Crystal Spider Eyes? I have them on my cleric, 8ac 3wis/int 35hp/mana, cheap as heck on my server too :)<br>
<br>
I have a full set of ToFS keys, but that camp is soooo boring. I've seen like 1 ring drop ever :( I'll probably have to do it though. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showPrevMessage?topicID=26421.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showNextMessage?topicID=26421.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26421.topic&index=7><img src=http://dev.thedruidsgrove.org/images/forum/addreplya.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.emailToFriend?topicID=26421.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.threadControl?topicID=26421.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/gfx/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=26421.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=26421.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thedruidsgrovegeneral">General - EQ<option value="thedruidsgrovegeneral